orah","name":"Utpal Borah","party":"Bharatiya Janata Party","sub":"Gohpur"},{"id":"rangapara-ac-as-krishna-kamal-tanti","name":"Krishna Kamal Tanti","party":"Bharatiya Janata Party","sub":"Rangapara"},{"id":"tezpur-ac-as-prithiraj-rava","name":"Prithiraj Rava","party":"Asom Gana Parishad","sub":"Tezpur"}],"mps":[{"id":"sonitpur-ranjit-dutta","name":"Ranjit Dutta","party":"Bharatiya Janata Party","sub":"Sonitpur"}],"portal":{"url":"https://sonitpur.assam.gov.in","whosWhoUrl":"https://sonitpur.assam.gov.in/whos-who","contactUrl":"https://sonitpur.assam.gov.in/contact-us","phone":"03712220011","email":"dc-sonitpur@nic.in","retrieved":"2026-07-15"}},"Tinsukia":{"officials":[],"mlas":[{"id":"digboi-ac-as-suren-phukan","name":"Suren Phukan","party":"Bharatiya Janata Party","sub":"Digboi"},{"id":"doom-dooma-ac-as-rupesh-gowala","name":"Rupesh Gowala","party":"Bharatiya Janata Party","sub":"Doom Dooma"},{"id":"margherita-ac-as-bhaskar-sharma","name":"Bhaskar Sharma","party":"Bharatiya Janata Party","sub":"Margherita"},{"id":"sadiya-ac-as-bolin-chetia","name":"Bolin Chetia","party":"Bharatiya Janata Party","sub":"Sadiya"},{"id":"tinsukia-ac-as-pulok-gohain","name":"Pulok Gohain","party":"Bharatiya Janata Party","sub":"Tinsukia"}],"mps":[{"id":"dibrugarh-sarbananda-sonowal","name":"Sarbananda Sonowal","party":"Bharatiya Janata Party","photo":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Chief%20Minister%20of%20Assam%20Sarbananda%20Sonowal.jpg?width=400","sub":"Dibrugarh"},{"id":"lakhimpur-pradan-baruah","name":"Pradan Baruah","party":"Bharatiya Janata Party","sub":"Lakhimpur"}],"portal":{"url":"https://tinsukia.assam.gov.in","whosWhoUrl":"https://tinsukia.assam.gov.in/whos-who","contactUrl":"https://tinsukia.assam.gov.in/contact-us","phone":"03742333642","email":"dc-tinsukia@nic.in","retrieved":"2026-07-15"}}},"channels":[{"kind":"url","topic":"general","label":"Assam State Portal (official state government homepage)","value":"https://assam.gov.in/","scope":"state","source_url":"https://assam.gov.in/","source_name":"Assam State Portal, Government of Assam","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Official unified state portal. Nodal department: General Administration, Assam Secretariat."},{"kind":"url","topic":"general","label":"Districts List - directory of all district websites","value":"https://assam.gov.in/districts-page.html","scope":"state","source_url":"https://assam.gov.in/districts-page.html","source_name":"Districts List | Assam State Portal","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Official state-portal page listing 33 districts, each linking to its own district website (e.g. kamrupmetro.assam.gov.in, cachar.gov.in)."},{"kind":"url","topic":"general","label":"District Websites directory (General Administration Dept)","value":"https://gad.assam.gov.in/district-websites","scope":"state","source_url":"https://gad.assam.gov.in/district-websites","source_name":"General Administration Department, Government of Assam","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Second official district directory with per-district URLs. Bajali and Tamulpur have no live link at time of check."},{"kind":"url","topic":"grievance","label":"Write to the Chief Minister (grievances/queries)","value":"https://cm.assam.gov.in/write-to-cm","scope":"state","source_url":"https://cm.assam.gov.in/write-to-cm","source_name":"Chief Minister of Assam - official website","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Assam does NOT publish a short-code CM helpline. Aggregator sites claiming '1100' for Assam are wrong - the NEGD directory entry behind that claim is Tamil Nadu's. Use this channel plus the CMO numbers instead."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"grievance","label":"Chief Minister's Office, Assam","value":"03612262222","scope":"state","source_url":"https://cm.assam.gov.in/write-to-cm","source_name":"Chief Minister of Assam - Write to CM","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Published on the CMO site and CM homepage. Office: Lok Sewa Bhawan, J Block, Janata Bhawan, Dispur, Guwahati 781006. Email cm@assam.gov.in"},{"kind":"phone","topic":"grievance","label":"Chief Minister's Office, Assam (alternate)","value":"03612237043","scope":"state","source_url":"https://cm.assam.gov.in/write-to-cm","source_name":"Chief Minister of Assam - Write to CM","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Second CMO line published on the same official page."},{"kind":"url","topic":"grievance","label":"Sewa Setu - Public Grievance Redressal service","value":"https://sewasetu.assam.gov.in/site/service-apply/public-grievance-redressal","scope":"state","source_url":"https://sewasetu.assam.gov.in/site/service-apply/public-grievance-redressal","source_name":"Sewa Setu, Government of Assam (ARTPS portal)","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"State citizen-services portal under the Assam RTPS Act 2012; grievance can be lodged and a report downloaded. NOTE: the Sewa Setu toll-free number (18003453574) is deliberately omitted - the portal itself states the helpline is temporarily unavailable and directs users to email."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"police","label":"Assam Police Citizen Portal helpline","value":"03612460303","scope":"state","source_url":"https://assampolice.assam.gov.in/citizen/login.aspx","source_name":"Assam Police Citizen Portal","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Published on the portal as 'Call us now (0361)-2460303'. This is the citizen-portal support line, not an emergency line - for emergencies use 112."},{"kind":"url","topic":"police","label":"Assam Police - official website","value":"https://police.assam.gov.in/","scope":"state","source_url":"https://police.assam.gov.in/","source_name":"Assam Police, Government of Assam","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Links to Seva Setu, e-Complaint, e-FIR and grievance redressal."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"police","label":"Assam Police Headquarters","value":"03612450555","scope":"state","source_url":"https://police.assam.gov.in/contact-us","source_name":"Assam Police - Contact Us","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Police HQ, Ulubari, Guwahati. Email dgp@assampolice.gov.in. No state-level control-room number is published on a fetchable official page; the Assam Police control-room listing page returns HTTP 403."},{"kind":"url","topic":"police","label":"Assam Police Seva Setu (online police services)","value":"https://polcitizen.assam.gov.in/","scope":"state","source_url":"https://polcitizen.assam.gov.in/","source_name":"Assam Police Seva Setu","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Online services: complaint filing, verifications, event permissions, grievance redressal."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"women","label":"Assam Women Helpline (Assam Police CID)","value":"9345215029","scope":"state","source_url":"https://police.assam.gov.in/frontimpotentdata/womens-rights-and-helpline","source_name":"Assam Police - Women's Rights and Helpline","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Assam-specific women's helpline run by Assam Police CID. Email ssp-cid@assampolice.gov.in with subject 'Helpline for Women'. Verified on two separate fetches of the official page."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"women","label":"Assam Women Helpline (landline, Assam Police CID)","value":"03612521242","scope":"state","source_url":"https://police.assam.gov.in/frontimpotentdata/womens-rights-and-helpline","source_name":"Assam Police - Women's Rights and Helpline","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Second Assam-specific women's helpline line published on the same official Assam Police page."},{"kind":"url","topic":"electricity","label":"APDCL - file an electricity complaint online (CGRF)","value":"https://www.apdcl.org/cgrf/noauth/fileComplaint","scope":"state","source_url":"https://www.apdcl.org/cgrf/noauth/fileComplaint","source_name":"Assam Power Distribution Company Limited (APDCL) - Consumer Grievance Redressal Forum","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Official DISCOM online complaint form (consumer number + OTP). Categories include interruption, voltage, load shedding, meter, bill, disconnection, new connection. The widely-quoted APDCL number 1912 is omitted: it appears only on aggregator sites and on JS-rendered APDCL pages that could not be fetched and read.","operator":"APDCL"},{"kind":"url","topic":"electricity","label":"AERC - how to file an electricity bill/service complaint","value":"https://aerc.assam.gov.in/how-to/file-complain-electricity-bill-or-service-connection","scope":"state","source_url":"https://aerc.assam.gov.in/how-to/file-complain-electricity-bill-or-service-connection","source_name":"Assam Electricity Regulatory Commission (AERC), Government of Assam","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Official escalation ladder: APDCL level 1-2, then CGRF (Tezpur, Dibrugarh, Jorhat, Silchar, Rangia, Bongaigaon, Nagaon, Guwahati), then Electricity Ombudsman.","operator":"AERC (Electricity Regulator)"},{"kind":"phone","topic":"electricity","label":"Assam Electricity Ombudsman","value":"03612234442","scope":"state","source_url":"https://aerc.assam.gov.in/how-to/file-complain-electricity-bill-or-service-connection","source_name":"Assam Electricity Regulatory Commission (AERC)","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Escalation body only - consumers must approach APDCL's CGRF first. Office at ASEB Campus, Sixth Mile, Guwahati.","operator":"Assam Electricity Ombudsman"},{"kind":"phone","topic":"emergency","label":"National Emergency Number (ERSS) - Police, Fire & Rescue, Health","value":"112","scope":"national","source_url":"https://www.mha.gov.in/en/commoncontent/emergency-response-support-system-erss","source_name":"Ministry of Home Affairs, Government of India","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"MHA's single pan-India emergency number: 'ONE INDIA ONE EMERGENCY NUMBER 112', a nationwide unified emergency response system. Works in every State/UT. Corroborated by india.gov.in helpline directory, which lists 112 as the Integrated Helpline (ERSS) covering Police, Fire & Rescue and Health services."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"fire","label":"Fire Helpline","value":"101","scope":"national","source_url":"https://www.india.gov.in/directory/helpline","source_name":"National Portal of India (india.gov.in), NIC / MeitY","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Listed under 'Emergency Numbers' on the National Portal of India helpline directory (page last reviewed/updated 14 July 2026)."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"ambulance","label":"National Ambulance Service (NAS)","value":"102","scope":"national","source_url":"https://www.india.gov.in/directory/helpline","source_name":"National Portal of India (india.gov.in), NIC / MeitY","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Listed as 'National Ambulance Service (NAS)' under Emergency Numbers on the National Portal of India helpline directory (page last reviewed/updated 14 July 2026)."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"women","label":"Women Helpline (national, toll-free)","value":"181","scope":"national","source_url":"https://wcd.gov.in/","source_name":"Ministry of Women and Child Development, Government of India","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Published as 'Women Helpline Toll free No. - 181' directly by the owning ministry (WCD) as a tel: link on its homepage. Also listed on india.gov.in as both 'Women Helpline Number' and 'Domestic Violence Helpline'."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"women","label":"National Commission for Women (NCW) 24x7 Helpline","value":"14490","scope":"national","source_url":"https://ncw.gov.in/","source_name":"National Commission for Women (NCW)","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"NCW's own site states: 'Call the 24x7 NCW helpline at 14490 for immediate assistance and support', and lists 'NCW Women Helpline (14490)' under its Complaint Redressal cells. IMPORTANT: the india.gov.in helpline directory still lists 7827170170 as the 'National Commission for Women Helpline' - that number appears nowhere on ncw.gov.in (not even in raw HTML), so it appears stale and was deliberately omitted in favour of the department's own current number."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"child","label":"Child Helpline (national, toll-free)","value":"1098","scope":"national","source_url":"https://wcd.gov.in/","source_name":"Ministry of Women and Child Development, Government of India","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Published as 'Child Helpline Toll free No. - 1098' directly by the owning ministry (WCD) as a tel: link on its homepage. Also listed as 'Child Help Line' on india.gov.in."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"senior","label":"Elderline - National Helpline for Senior Citizens (NHSC)","value":"14567","scope":"national","source_url":"https://scw.dosje.gov.in/elderline","source_name":"Department of Social Justice & Empowerment, Government of India","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Published as 'Elder Helpline: 14567' on the Department of Social Justice & Empowerment's own Elderline site, which the ministry homepage links to as the 'National Helpline for Senior Citizens (NHSC)'. india.gov.in additionally lists a landline 011-20893999 alongside 14567 for the Senior Citizens Helpline."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"grievance","label":"National Consumer Helpline (NCH)","value":"1915","scope":"national","source_url":"https://www.india.gov.in/directory/helpline","source_name":"National Portal of India (india.gov.in), NIC / MeitY","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Listed as 'National Consumer Helpline (NCH)' on the National Portal of India helpline directory (page last reviewed/updated 14 July 2026). Note: the NCH portal consumerhelpline.gov.in could not be reached at time of research (DNS resolves to an NIC address but the host refused connections / returned 504), so only the number is cited here - not the NCH portal URL."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"cyber","label":"Cyber Crime Helpline (online financial fraud reporting)","value":"1930","scope":"national","source_url":"https://cybercrime.gov.in/","source_name":"National Cyber Crime Reporting Portal, MHA / I4C","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Confirmed on the National Cyber Crime Reporting Portal homepage banner (MHA / Indian Cyber Crime Coordination Centre - I4C), which reads: 'To report online financial fraud, call 1930' and 'register your complaint at cybercrime.gov.in'. Independently corroborated by the india.gov.in helpline directory, which lists 1930 as the Cyber Crime Helpline."},{"kind":"url","topic":"cyber","label":"National Cyber Crime Reporting Portal (file a cybercrime complaint)","value":"https://cybercrime.gov.in/","scope":"national","source_url":"https://cybercrime.gov.in/","source_name":"National Cyber Crime Reporting Portal, MHA / I4C","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Verified live. Ministry of Home Affairs portal for reporting cybercrime; supports anonymous reporting, women/children-related crime, financial fraud and other cybercrime, plus complaint tracking. Nationwide."},{"kind":"url","topic":"grievance","label":"CPGRAMS - Centralised Public Grievance Redress and Monitoring System","value":"https://pgportal.gov.in/","scope":"national","source_url":"https://pgportal.gov.in/","source_name":"Ministry of Personnel, Public Grievances & Pensions, Government of India","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Verified live; this is the citizen-facing portal. The site states CPGRAMS is 'an online platform available to the citizens 24x7 to lodge their grievances to the public authorities on any subject related to service delivery... a single portal connected to all the Ministries/Departments of Government of India and States.' Supports tracking by registration ID and an appeal facility. Note: it does not cover RTI matters, subjudice/court matters, or religious matters."},{"kind":"url","topic":"corruption","label":"Central Vigilance Commission - lodge a corruption complaint","value":"https://portal.cvc.gov.in/","scope":"national","source_url":"https://portal.cvc.gov.in/","source_name":"Central Vigilance Commission (CVC), Government of India","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Verified live. CVC's Complaint Management System with a 'Citizen Login', complaint status tracking and a published complaint handling policy. Linked from cvc.gov.in as 'Lodge a complaint'. Covers corruption complaints against central government organisations."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"disaster","label":"Relief Commissioner for Natural Calamities","value":"1070","scope":"national","source_url":"https://www.india.gov.in/directory/helpline","source_name":"National Portal of India (india.gov.in), NIC / MeitY","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Listed on the National Portal of India helpline directory (page last reviewed/updated 14 July 2026)."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"road","label":"Road Accident Helpline","value":"1073","scope":"national","source_url":"https://www.india.gov.in/directory/helpline","source_name":"National Portal of India (india.gov.in), NIC / MeitY","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Listed on the National Portal of India helpline directory (page last reviewed/updated 14 July 2026)."}]}